}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The '''Linksys''' support page states there is one version with information available (v2.0), but I don't know if there are actually multiple revisions of this device. The device used to populate this entry has a S/N of AC1A13802162. :The device pictured in '''Linksys''''s User Guide (copyright year is 2002) has a strip with '''ProConnect''' ''USB 4-Port Hub'' '''USB 2.0''' or something on it.. this is not on my device.
"M01-UH402-A10" is silkscreened on the board. :This would seem to be an '''AboCom''' UH402.
The power adapter included with the device may be a '''Honor Electronic''' ADS-0521PCD (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.3A max. -> 5VDC 2.1A).
